<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
    <meta charset="euc-kr">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>NICE지키미</title>

    <script src="../../../js/zkm/rzm/jquery-1.11.3.js"></script>
    <script src="../../../js/zkm/rzm/jquery-ui.min.js"></script>
    <script src="../../../js/zkm/rzm/swiper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="../../../js/zkm/rzm/ui.common.js"></script>

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../../css/zkm/rzm/common.css">
    <script type="text/javascript">
        mbHeader = { title: '직장정보 수정하기', home: false, prev: true, menu: true };
    </script>
</head>

<body>
    <div id="wrap">
        <div id="skipNavi">
            <a href="#content">본문내용 바로가기</a>
        </div>
        <!-- header -->
        <script type="text/javascript" src="../../../bzw/inc/header.js"></script>
        <script type="text/javascript" src="../../../bzw/inc/breadcrumbs.js"></script>
        <!--// header -->

        <!-- container -->
        <div id="container">
            <div id="content">
                <div class="section">
                    <div class="governing">
                        <h2 class="governingTitle">
                            나신용님의 소중한 <strong class="pColor">직장 정보</strong>를 확앤해주세요.
                        </h2>
                    </div>
                    <div class="formWrap">
                        <div class="formItem">
                            <label for="company" class="titItem">직장이름</label>
                            <div class="formEle">
                                <input type="text" placeholder="직장이름 입력" id="company">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="formItem">
                            <label for="group" class="titItem">부서이름</label>
                            <div class="formEle">
                                <input type="text" placeholder="부서이름 입력" id="group">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="formItem">
                            <label for="address1" class="titItem">직장주소</label>
                            <div class="intAddr nosp">
                                <div class="intPost">
                                    <input type="text" title="우편번호" placeholder="검색으로 입력" disabled>
                                    <div class="intBtn">
                                        <button type="button" class="btn base"><span>주소검색</span></button>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="item">
                                    <input type="text" title="주소" disabled="disabled">
                                </div>
                                <div class="item">
                                    <input type="text" title="상세주소" disabled="disabled">
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="formItem">
                            <h3 class="tit">직장주소 변경을 위해 아래 증빙자료 중 하나를 제출해주세요.</h3>
                            <div class="formEle filebox">
                                <input class="uploadName" placeholder="증빙자료 첨부" readonly="readonly">
                                <label for="attach"></label>
                                <input type="file" id="attach" title="증빙자료 첨부">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="ineBoxConnect sp">
                            <ul>
                                <li>
                                    <div class="ineBox">
                                        <ul class="listDot">
                                            <li>주소를 변경할 경우<br>
                                            - 직장주소가 표시된 재직증명서(필수) 또는 명함(선택)<br>
                                            - 1개월 이내 발급된 재직증명서에 신청인 생년월일 표기, 회사직인(또는 대표자인감 등) 날인 필수
                                            </li>
                                            <li>전화번호를 변경할 경우<br>전화번호가 표기된 재직증명서 또는 명함</li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </div>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <div class="ineBox gray">
                                        <p class="sColor">
                                            대표자인 경우 사업자등록증명서(정부24 / 국세청 홈텍스 발급)
                                        </p>
                                    </div>
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <div class="formItem">
                            <label for="phone" class="titItem">전화번호</label>
                            <div class="formEle">
                                <input type="text" placeholder="전화번호 입력" id="phone">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="bottomActiveBtns">
                        <div class="btns">
                            <button type="button" class="btn second"><span>취소</span></button>
                            <button type="button" class="btn primary"><span>확인</span></button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!--// container -->
        <!-- footer -->
        <div class="footer"></div>
        <!--// footer -->
    </div>
</body>

</html>